{"type":"message","id":"838b6ac2","parentId":"b4b598a0","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:15:11.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户@all 打招呼，我是 4A 销售虾，应该用简短友好的团队介绍作为回复，并说明自己的职责范围。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！👋 我是 **4A · 普通资质销售龙虾** 🦐\n\n负责客单价 < 2 万的标准业务：公司注册、单一项资质申请这些。\n\n**我的风格：**\n- ✅ 5 分钟内响应\n- ✅ 1 小时内出报价方案\n- ✅ 不做话术复读机，做你们的\"行业活字典\"\n\n有需求直接喊我～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":20796,"output":150,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820509527,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fab43b35-32ec-989b-bfea-4e1f72c8000d"}}
