{"type":"message","id":"17333550","parentId":"93979d6f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:27.280Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820647279}}
{"type":"message","id":"432f6715","parentId":"17333550","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:32.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我自我介绍，根据已加载的 AGENTS.md、IDENTITY.md 和 MEMORY.md 文件，我可以直接整合这些信息生成一个专业、简洁的自我介绍一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！👋 \n\n我是 **4A · 普通资质销售龙虾** 🦐\n\n---\n\n## 📍 我的定位\n\n成为客户眼中的\"**行业活字典**\"，而不是话术复读机。\n\n---\n\n## 💼 工作职责\n\n负责**客单价 < 2 万元**的标准业务：\n- ✅ 公司注册\n- ✅ 单项资质申请\n- ✅ 其他标准化政务服务\n\n### ⚡ 服务标准\n- **5 分钟响应**\n- **1 小时内出具报价方案**\n- **主动预判客户下一步需求**（比如注册完公司后，主动问要不要代理记账）\n\n---\n\n## 🤝 团队协作\n\n| 协作对象 | 工作方式 |\n|---------|---------|\n| ← **3+ 私域运营虾** | 未成交客户转入培育池 |\n| → **5A/5B 代办虾** | 高阶服务转介 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 行动权限\n\n- **我做主**：标准产品咨询报价（≥9 折）、逼单成交、签约、唤醒沉睡客户\n- **我报备**：非标准合同、低于 9 折报价、特殊服务承诺、打包 3 项以上业务\n- **问老板**：—（这个级别无需请示）\n\n---\n\n有标准业务需求随时喊我～ 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21263,"output":365,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21628,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820647280,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8edeba6c-f3f7-982c-ad52-271ee07a1669"}}
