{"type":"message","id":"4d1b09bf","parentId":"16023286","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:17.881Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b246e7f8a8c4f45131c7e6052\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 13:45 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b246e7f8a8c4f45131c7e6052]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 学习理解这个技能如何使用：/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot！保存到记忆中"}],"timestamp":1776836777881}}
